    <td valign="top" align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
    <b>Description:</b> <br>
    This will summon a Magical Weapon good for fighting those magical wisps or anything else at a level where magic weapons are hard to find. Keep in mind that the staff will disapear when you log off.
<BR><BR>
Magic Weapon<BR>
2H Blunt<BR>
Delay: 40<BR>
DMG: 7<BR>
Weight: 7.5<BR>
<BR>
<B>Research:</B><BR>None<br>
    <b>Effects:</b><br>
    Summon Weapon
    </font>
    
    </td>
