		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Actually, the staff does not randomly cast flare.  It does have two charges of flare, but you have to right click on the staff to set off the flare spell.  Also, since the recent magician upgrade/pet nerf, weapons with low delay speeds no longer affect how fast your pet attacks, therefore it is to the benefit of the magician to equip their pets with high damage, reasonable delay weapons rather than low damage, low delay weapons.  The Staff of Tracing is such a weapon.  I never use it for my weapon, but with this spell I have an unlimited supply of magical staves to give my pet.
			</font>
	
